											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Down on street level. Various Baldurians cower or stand ready to defend themselves from Mind Flayers. They grimace, awaiting the final assault... &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;... but it does not come. The Mind Flayers no longer attack, but keep the survivors surrounded, watching and waiting.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The Baldurians look up in terror and awe as a huge shadow falls." />
