									<children>
										<node id="data" key="key">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The Netherbrain's descent slows as it nears street level. Damaged buildings tremble, and a great cloud of dust fills the air. The watching Mind Flayers part ranks. From the dust cloud -&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- The Enthralled Companions stride forth. They clear a path to the Baldurians like an honour guard. A final figure floats downwards as the dust settles. The Player. Psionics pulse outwards from the player. All those around them, including Enthralled Companions, kneel. All save for Love Interest Minthara, if present. She approaches the player's side." />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
						</node>
